  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_10",
    "text": "E5.3各加4mL乙酸乙酯，加塞振摇50次，离心5min，取出静置分层。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12606837606837606,
