    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_book_zh_GB115041989_extracted_page_9_11",
    "text": "E5.4各取2mL乙酸乙酯萃取液，于另外6支10mL具塞比色管中，各加改良显色剂2mL，加塞振 摇，静置10min。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12713675213675213,
      0.49634482103864047,
      0.8979700854700855,
      0.5343207063514668
    ],
